          Sdcp Monitor
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
          Copyright (c) 2024 Jeroen Walter<LineBreak />
          License:<Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/jeroenwalter/SdcpMonitor?tab=MIT-1-ov-file">MIT</Hyperlink>
          <LineBreak />
